{"tid":1615710,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我女朋友因為我老母同我講分手","createTime":"2019-10-03T07:35:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T04:07:27.000Z","uid":251238,"like":8,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"09bf22e90eb7dd6daf2c62ecd23930fbb5d80973","tid":1615710,"uid":251238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:35:52.000Z","msg":"我女朋友同我老母本身都係一個終極港女同超級公主<br />\n一齊咗年半<br />\n我老母開到聲叫我帶女友上泥食餐飯見下家長<br />\n尋晚終於成事<br />\n點知一埋位食飯就出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我老母用佢慣常既方法 夾舊餸比我<br />\n我已經即刻遞隻碗出去同佢講唔該阿媽<br />\n點知佢話：傻豬 平時都係餵落你口架啦 呀～<br />\n想叫我Mark 大口接佢舊肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n空氣凝結左幾秒<br />\n為咗唔想老母唔開心<br />\n我於是用口接咗我老母舊肉<br />\n當時我錨咗我女朋友一眼<br />\n已經見佢塊面黑到 dup 低個頭粒聲唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n未打完 一陣繼續"},{"pid":"d3cc2dad2d26085e9096ef5f894e1f18ee205204","tid":1615710,"uid":297305,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:37:58.000Z","msg":"你食你阿媽嘅畀你嘅餸有乜嘢問題呀"},{"pid":"05520b9a58a956a683d446eb4e2bbf46c86e9d37","tid":1615710,"uid":269681,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:39:33.000Z","msg":"潮文黎？"},{"pid":"109932841317b70dc6872bd9735fa591c805a931","tid":1615710,"uid":251238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05520b9a58a956a683d446eb4e2bbf46c86e9d37","tid":1615710,"uid":269681,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:39:33.000Z","msg":"潮文黎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:53:05.000Z","msg":"唔係<br />\n係我真人真事泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等等我返緊工<br />\n要擠d 時間出泥打埋落去"},{"pid":"dae495b9414131a8089bd5d060804243b89a3253","tid":1615710,"uid":33004,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:55:39.000Z","msg":"下一秒你老母露左兩隻奶出黎<br />\n你係你條女面前啜曬你老母兩隻奶<br />\n仲啜到流曬口水"},{"pid":"aa6acf26726f69163a6715f06fbaff697f489edd","tid":1615710,"uid":260934,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:02:56.000Z","msg":"哇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係要分手"},{"pid":"1956c3690b3e8f437d8226cef363cb4e33100f71","tid":1615710,"uid":39668,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:02:59.000Z","msg":"樓主今年有10歲未?"},{"pid":"4e964e4dfa53b024d25d20fc173da76f9d61c3c3","tid":1615710,"uid":251238,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"1956c3690b3e8f437d8226cef363cb4e33100f71","tid":1615710,"uid":39668,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:02:59.000Z","msg":"樓主今年有10歲未?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:13:23.000Z","msg":"夠<br />\n不過老母成日覺得我未戒奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84f71ba2048fb2b4cba1747340b507763c1cc489","tid":1615710,"uid":238589,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05520b9a58a956a683d446eb4e2bbf46c86e9d37","tid":1615710,"uid":269681,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:39:33.000Z","msg":"潮文黎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:58:33.000Z","msg":"將會係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d908e909b84eac81be7613b0158ccf02f58d6478","tid":1615710,"uid":251238,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T12:10:15.000Z","msg":"繼續<br />\n<br />\n到食完飯<br />\n我地就移師去客廳嗰邊坐啦<br />\n點知我老母一野得喺我同我女朋友中間 都算<br />\n我老母開始同我女朋友講起我兒時趣事<br />\n講到興起仲爆埋我好鐘意將個頭埋落佢對波度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我女朋友原本嘅笑容變到愈來愈僵<br />\n因為我女朋友係ipad 嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲未打完<br />\n食完飯繼續"},{"pid":"0bc9254cfd6e3ab6162556e22c1a08f688457a6e","tid":1615710,"uid":304508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:30:26.000Z","msg":"屌 我係囡都同你分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3667de8a93a624338031725b91a4afa1179551ab","tid":1615710,"uid":113007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T00:45:40.000Z","msg":"見到港童即走啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5fc2dba5ca73f763042de2b8fa6f1f85592125","tid":1615710,"uid":263534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T00:51:57.000Z","msg":"老母宣示主權<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66d4bbdbca1028e606ffd70344c4c8df944892d5","tid":1615710,"uid":41984,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:02:39.000Z","msg":"請用不推文回覆<br />\n有人仲係醫院訓緊<br />\n有人等提堂<br />\n有人等坐監<br />\n有人隻眼番唔到轉頭<br />\n珍惜熱門post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"152adbf455a4bd74e6a2e22f66f4d8089d01eeec","tid":1615710,"uid":251238,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:55:22.000Z","msg":"再繼續<br />\n<br />\n為左挽回女友嘅信任<br />\n我拉咗女友入房 諗住同佢兩個人傾傾<br />\n入到房 我女友即刻粒聲唔出衝去床邊坐<br />\n兩隻眼啲眼淚浪吓浪吓咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我見到佢咁可憐 即刻抱住佢安慰佢<br />\n佢問我 喺我心目中 佢重要啲定我老母<br />\n我緊係答佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢聽到我答案 即刻成個人軟曬咁訓喺我度<br />\n跟住我就開始錫佢<br />\n聽到佢開始呼吸急速 塊面又紅卜卜<br />\n我忍唔住開始除佢衫啲鈕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然佢係ipad 但佢兩粒lin好pink 好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就開始奶落去 聽到佢喘哂氣又細細聲叫出黎<br />\n我就叫佢細聲啲 老豆老母喺曬出面廳<br />\n當時個氣氛好刺激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好長 轉頭再打"},{"pid":"18264a66c21a9744ec9f6bedecfcd88fb2d5c235","tid":1615710,"uid":251238,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:57:27.000Z","msg":"跟著落黎好多甜 唔想知我可以skip 咗佢直接到結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdbc10c7d9c3109ad12b7d0918ab61099320b34c","tid":1615710,"uid":13333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:58:11.000Z","msg":"你屌你老母 放過條女"},{"pid":"b5ea319e690dd6ec0650d884c1a23eb65df1c4df","tid":1615710,"uid":251238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdbc10c7d9c3109ad12b7d0918ab61099320b34c","tid":1615710,"uid":13333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:58:11.000Z","msg":"你屌你老母 放過條女"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:59:41.000Z","msg":"點解"},{"pid":"76ff3c33ea1e21bd1aff1ebab40112072de41835","tid":1615710,"uid":158977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"152adbf455a4bd74e6a2e22f66f4d8089d01eeec","tid":1615710,"uid":251238,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:55:22.000Z","msg":"再繼續<br />\n<br />\n為左挽回女友嘅信任<br />\n我拉咗女友入房 諗住同佢兩個人傾傾<br />\n入到房 我女友即刻粒聲唔出衝去床邊坐<br />\n兩隻眼啲眼淚浪吓浪吓咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我見到佢咁可憐 即刻抱住佢安慰佢<br />\n佢問我 喺我